Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:08.19,sora-ep-title,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,430)}From the Starting Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:12.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.93,0:00:16.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The saucer over the city,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.15,0:00:21.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, who watched over us from nearby.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.93,0:00:24.50,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,All of it was real?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.57,0:00:26.75,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.53,0:00:29.58,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.04,0:00:31.15,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.87,0:00:35.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,No one remembers Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.95,0:00:38.20,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.32,0:00:42.84,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad you remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:46.49,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Just knowing I'm not the only one...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.70,0:00:48.41,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really satisfied with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.25,0:00:53.84,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,This girl I knew, Nonoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.07,0:00:59.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,would never give up on anything \Nshe set out to do until the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.62,0:01:01.54,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,She was honest and true.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.60,0:01:07.54,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Before we knew it, she'd have \Nchanged everyone's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.26,0:01:09.46,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.89,0:01:14.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,That's what this friend of mine was like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.22,0:01:16.55,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Am I wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.48,0:01:20.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.32,0:01:29.53,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,But it's...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.74,0:01:45.20,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm one of the people who was \Nchanged by Nonoka's willpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.44,0:01:50.33,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Have faith in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:56.35,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, can I ask you to do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:58.59,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.58,0:02:03.47,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want to get together with \Nour observatory friends once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.21,0:02:06.17,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:51.37,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Why you little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.53,0:03:52.50,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:56.63,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.79,0:04:11.98,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.77,0:04:16.74,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I've been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.13,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Shione, is that you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.10,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Koharu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.39,0:04:29.32,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.40,0:04:39.09,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka's back, and to \Nthink Shione's back, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.41,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,That's not quite it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:45.09,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,My school's still on summer break.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.25,0:04:46.64,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Vacation, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.75,0:04:48.20,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,That's a bit disappointing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:50.97,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping we could \Nbe together again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.59,0:04:53.68,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:55.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:57.44,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What're you up to this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:04:59.86,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,getting Shione involved?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:06.68,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all get together at the \Nobservatory one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.13,0:05:08.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Like last time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.46,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.27,0:05:14.37,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,We did try to call the saucer \Nlike you wanted us to,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.83,0:05:16.54,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,but the saucer never came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.52,0:05:19.25,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,How would I know \Nanything about Noel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:20.91,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.68,0:05:24.26,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.37,0:05:27.04,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know anything about Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.71,0:05:29.44,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:32.26,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ignore it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.27,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.31,0:05:40.27,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get what Nonoka \Nsaid out of my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.91,0:05:44.92,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always looking for memories \Nof a girl I don't even know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.99,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Even though there's \Nno way I'd find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.74,0:05:50.03,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Over and over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.86,0:05:55.39,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.75,0:05:57.73,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.85,0:05:59.04,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.25,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Something's totally missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.89,0:06:06.30,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Koharu, Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.95,0:06:08.76,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.24,0:06:13.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know we lost something important,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.54,0:06:15.81,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't remember what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.94,0:06:19.40,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.24,0:06:22.53,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:25.97,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,That we're all the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:30.91,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki, Koharu, Souta,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:35.66,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,me, and Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:40.11,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We must all be connected \Nby the same thoughts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.67,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,since that time
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.78,0:06:44.67,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,seven years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:49.59,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.78,0:06:54.08,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Before we completely \Nlose something important
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:55.81,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.97,0:07:01.95,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.97,0:07:08.27,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's call the saucer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:17.76,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.88,0:07:19.83,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember it being so wrecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:22.12,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:35.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,The time we spent here as kids
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.03,0:07:39.21,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.32,0:07:48.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel loved seeing us smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.16,0:07:54.07,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.49,0:07:58.99,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a bit embarrassed, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.48,0:08:00.73,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:01.87,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I am, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.31,0:08:03.38,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.73,0:08:07.01,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,You used to be pretty \Nbold in public, Yuzuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.12,0:08:07.96,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:13.97,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm curious, too, about \Nwhat the other Yuzuki did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:17.52,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.65,0:08:18.41,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:20.09,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I want to meet Noel-chan, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.24,0:08:21.98,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,To be with Noel one more time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:25.76,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, can you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.69,0:08:28.23,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We all want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.12,0:08:32.74,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,That's what we're all wishing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.84,0:08:34.80,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.77,0:09:18.57,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione's hat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.67,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,But we finally got to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.86,0:10:13.05,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here for a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:15.32,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you staying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.44,0:10:16.13,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.66,0:10:19.30,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I asked if she wanted to stay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.01,0:10:21.30,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:22.42,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.51,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:25.38,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Come to the shop, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.53,0:10:27.27,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,I will. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.34,0:10:31.95,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,But are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:34.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Dad will be fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.71,0:10:38.28,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,He was totally fine with Noel, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.83,0:10:49.90,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:30.40,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:33.10,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,make me a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:38.38,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, you're going to grow \Nup experiencing many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:43.22,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Of all those things, some of them \Nare going to be sad or painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.83,0:11:48.22,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,But at times like those, \Nespecially at times like those,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.64,0:11:51.09,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,you have to have the \Nbiggest smile you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.21,0:11:55.53,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,That way, you can get over anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.11,0:11:57.48,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:12:00.60,sora-flashback,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're my Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.84,0:12:02.99,sora-flashback,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.42,0:12:10.61,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Shione.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.34,0:12:12.45,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:17.60,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,When I was a kid, I saw a \Ngirl sitting here alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.66,0:12:20.25,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And I thought to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.03,0:12:23.86,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to be friends \Nwith her no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:28.01,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,And that if I didn't become her friend, \NI'd regret it for the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.87,0:12:33.39,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad it was you I met that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:36.44,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:45.49,Nozo,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Nozomitei
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:30.58,Kirigon,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Kirigon
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.00,0:14:19.92,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.69,0:14:35.06,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.44,0:14:36.26,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:37.71,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You're finally up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:40.22,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.34,0:14:41.94,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She had business in Hokubi City.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.37,0:14:44.20,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,She left a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.36,0:14:45.34,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:47.47,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,There, done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.97,0:14:51.09,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Omelette rice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:51.82,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.25,0:14:53.91,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,I had a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.14,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,From Shione?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.14,0:14:58.46,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,No, what was her name?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.37,0:15:01.80,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? She was here until just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.00,0:15:08.33,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Was she sitting in Mom's chair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:09.84,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.84,0:15:11.89,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:13.04,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.65,0:15:23.69,sora-main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,So no one's going to eat this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:42.33,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm the only one \Nthat remembers Noel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.39,0:15:45.95,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,then if I forget Noel,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:49.45,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,she might really disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.54,0:15:51.40,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.67,0:15:56.38,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to record everything \NI know about Noel.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:12.86,Orientation,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hokubi City High School\N{\fs16}Orientation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.54,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,We'll always be friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:54.62,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Such a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.69,0:17:03.04,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:05.14,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.55,Saucers,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Saucers Welcome
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.67,0:17:12.55,sora-main,Text,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:17.02,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to ignore me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.14,0:17:19.18,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,"No saucer" was better.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.31,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Onii-chan, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.58,0:17:23.98,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.62,0:17:38.20,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get better right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.11,0:17:40.80,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,You're a boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.76,0:17:57.22,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.62,0:18:00.42,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Monster-san will be always be well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.59,0:18:01.80,sora-internal,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.14,0:18:14.28,sora-main,Yuzuki,0000,0000,0000,,Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:15.94,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Want a ride?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.85,0:18:18.84,sora-main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.46,0:18:21.96,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:25.62,sora-main,Koharu,0000,0000,0000,,I have to go find your lost friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.05,0:18:49.84,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,There's still so much \Nmore I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.34,0:18:54.52,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,So many memories I want to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.00,0:18:57.74,sora-internal,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Noel, I miss you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.96,0:19:03.00,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,We'll see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.52,0:22:51.56,sora-main,Shione,0000,0000,0000,,Nonoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:56.37,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.80,0:22:58.85,sora-main,Nonoka,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Noel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.91,0:23:20.09,sora-main,Noel,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.09,0:23:24.09,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.09,0:23:26.09,sora-main,,0000,0000,0000,,
